cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Perseus in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Perseus: LLM-Assisted Binary Deobfuscation"
abstract: "Perseus is a LoRA fine-tuned large language model for x86-64 binary deobfuscation. It investigates the feasibility of adapting instruction-tuned code models for binary deobfuscation, a core challenge in static malware analysis where obfuscation is routinely used to evade detection and complicate attribution."
authors:
